    dc:creator "Subedi, Madan" ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "A new genus and a new groundhopper species from Nepal (Orthoptera: Tetriginae Skejotettix netrajyoti gen. et sp. nov.)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285841>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285847>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285851> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285841>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Investigated localities from different parts of Nepal: A—Bhottar khola, Ghyalchok, Gorkha; B—Buldikhola, Vyas, Tanahun; C—Tirtire khola, Ghyalchok, Gorkha; D—Ghadiyal Breeding Center, Kasara, Chitwan; E—Umari, Shivaraj, Kapilvastu; F—Shree Netrajyoti Basic School, Churlingtar, Ghyalchok, Gorkha and adjacent Sal forest; G-H—Type locality, subtropical Sal forest, Churlingtar, Ghyalchok, Gorkha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285841/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285847>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Hainantettix spp.: A-C—H. strictivertex; D—H. angustivertex (Zha et Peng, 2021) comb. nov.; E-H—H. hainanensis (Liang, 2002) comb. nov. Images were taken from iNaturalist with the permission of corresponding authors (imagesA–C courtesy of Fan Gao, username: xiaodoudou and images D–H courtesy of Ruiyang Wang, username: seventeennature)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285847/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7285851>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lateral view of some tetrigids with a notch on the scapus of the antenna (indicated by a white arrow): A—Skejotettix netrajyoti gen. et sp. nov.; B—Skejotettix muglingi comb. nov.; C—Ergatettix dorsiferus; D—Coptotettix annandalei; E— Coptotettix coniopticus" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7285851/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

